import * as React from "react";

const CasterLogo = (props) => (
  <svg
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    xmlnsXlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
    width="120"
    height="40"
    fill="none"
    viewBox="0 0 120 36"
    preserveAspectRatio="none"
  >
    <path fill="url(#pattern0_7592_78464)" d="M.5 0h119v36H.5z"></path>
    <defs>
      <pattern
        id="pattern0_7592_78464"
        width="1"
        height="1"
        patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox"
      >
        <use
          xlinkHref="#image0_7592_78464"
          transform="matrix(.00044 0 0 .00145 0 -.007)"
        ></use>
      </pattern>
      <image
        xlinkHref="data:image/jpeg;base64,"
        id="image0_7592_78464"
        width="2281"
        height="700"
      ></image>
    </defs>
  </svg>
);

export default CasterLogo;
